		<div>Main focus of the next expansion for wizards should hands down be : increased mana regen ability specific to wizards via our flappy &amp; Harvest - Next would be the Extention of silent casting and refresh lockout shortened ~ With those improvements wizards could maintain steady dps on current encounters and have the mana to stay in step with other classes, such as a necro who has over 100FT with new lich...:wtf: <br />
<br />
<ul><li>Improve familiar from Devoted : Mana regen  [15 ft] &amp; +10 increase to all resists (10) AA</li><li>Harvest of Druzzil needs to be increased to at least 1k mana pool boost 2 levels (3/6) AA</li><li>Hasten &amp; Extend Silent casting to  3 minutes also include a 100% hate reduction to final level *not random (3/6/9) AA</li><li>Add 2 levels to Hasten Mind Crash refresh should max out at every three minutes (3/6) AA</li></ul></div>
